{"tid":1849922,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"好想投訴政府處理疫情手法","createTime":"2020-01-29T09:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T14:47:42.000Z","uid":149978,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"629cd2425ad56ccccd5b7a44d3ffd69962343909","tid":1849922,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:49:47.000Z","msg":"一開始太低調，知出事一黎就全民戴口罩，全城停服務，搞到無晒口罩。有時唔戴口罩出街，都被人歧視或屌，為社交原因唔想戴口罩都要罩<br />\n<br />\n應該<br />\n1）確保醫護有口罩<br />\n2）之後疫情擴散，應該出力鼓勵一些需要「長期對人的工作」的員工，如顧客服務員、酒店員工、食市員工、老師、社工輔導、SALES等戴口罩。<br />\n3）再擴散全面罷工，好似今日咁<br />\n4）再擴散要封關<br />\n5）全民戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題政府skip左step 2直跳入step 5<br />\n<br />\n全民戴口罩要確保有足夠口罩，淨香港計都係碼要三億個，冇足夠口罩的，唔該你快些封關好過啦。"},{"pid":"58f8ba75b89e15741846a7952f20c7cd16b4b1c0","tid":1849922,"uid":122275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:52:18.000Z","msg":"投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132ce5c8be1177fae73912b0a0a598e38fee15f8","tid":1849922,"uid":50776,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"醒未呀 投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想投訴政府既唯一途徑我唸剩係可以返大陸搵小熊維尼投訴 一係你試下？"},{"pid":"e45f96259b586142d6f10412acf071703b97803d","tid":1849922,"uid":66242,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:19:04.000Z","msg":"訓咗七個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb22912ff4b594bc6b3ce2393a555261eea5649","tid":1849922,"uid":127067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:20:04.000Z","msg":"投訴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱啱放出黎？"},{"pid":"68674ba8e8ff50129260782d06ca22e09d3381d5","tid":1849922,"uid":289946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:20:08.000Z","msg":"同邊個投訴？共產黨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p